SIEMENS SUSTAINABILIT Y REPORT 2023 77

Siemens Mobility enables transportation operators around the world to make their trains and infrastructure smart and electrified, and contributes to efficient, low-carbon transpor- tation. Leveraging the advantages of digitalization, it helps increase sustainable value creation throughout the entire lifecycle, improve passenger comfort, deliver 100% system availability, and maximize network capacity.

The Siemens Mobility portfolio is almost fully eligible, contributing to climate change mitigation through manufac- turing of low-carbon technologies for transportation, and providing infrastructure for rail transportation and infra- structure enabling public transport.